ِهِ", "tr": "rabbihi", "m": "(of) his Lord"}, {"t": "ٱلْأَعْلَىٰ", "tr": "l-aʿlā", "m": "the Most High"}], "21": [{"t": "وَلَسَوْفَ", "tr": "walasawfa", "m": "And soon, surely"}, {"t": "يَرْضَىٰ", "tr": "yarḍā", "m": "he will be pleased"}]}